data.description: Come check out this Stunning, well cared for 5 bedroom, 3 bath home with 3 additional bonus rooms! This green belt, no back neighbor home has a pocket room at master, a bonus room upstairs, one bedroom downstairs plus an office. Home is also on a culdesac street. Blanco Vista master planned community has its own elementary school plus pool and splashpad. Zoned for Hays ISD. There is an abundance of walking trails and right across from 5-mile dam.
